data.description: Why wait for new when you can have new-ish without the price tag? This home was built in 2020, and feels never-lived-in. 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a split bedroom floor plan allows for all the living without the hassle of being in everyone else's way. Located on a spacious corner lot in the newly developed Moody Estate subdivision, this home features an open concept kitchen and living room so you can always be in the action. The kitchen has custom Maple cabinets, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and an island you can pull stools up to as a breakfast bar. The living room has high trey ceilings, French doors leading out to the fenced backyard, and neutral paint. Wood-look tile throughout the common areas, newer carpet in the bedrooms, and modern paint throughout the whole home. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet, two windows for plenty of natural light, and an en suite with double sinks. Indoor laundry room with a folding table, two-car garage, easy to maintain siding, three-year old appliances, roof, and HVAC, and No HOA. Located 10 minutes to NSB Kings Bay, close to I-95 and anywhere in town you need to be.
